Module org.nasdanika.architecture.c4
Package org.nasdanika.architecture.c4

Interface C4Package.Literals

Enclosing interface:
C4Package
public static interface C4Package.Literals
Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each operation of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
